    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything i've ever made just feels like noise now. i look at my studio and i just see... nothing. it's like the well went dry and it's never coming back. i've spent my whole life chasing this spark and now that it's gone, i don't even know what i'm supposed to do with the rest of my time here.",
