    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"find a new way to fill the emptiness\"... what if there isn't one? i feel like i've tried every path, every technique, every distraction. it's not just a creative block. it feels more fundamental. like the reason for being here was the art, and without it, i'm just a shell going through the motions. what is the point of just existing if there's nothing left to give?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
